{"tid":2396313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府宣布所有由外國回港本地機組人員由本月20日起（20/2）必須於指定酒店隔離14天及接受7天醫學監察方可再次執勤！","createTime":"2021-02-05T13:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T16:00:45.000Z","uid":63113,"like":14,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"a62f9cd7ef8111bd88f995b6bda24b738b418e74","tid":2396313,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:15:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad3e6fd66ae4f8ff9cbbde04dc05a9f24fc9275","tid":2396313,"uid":63113,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:16:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EY6B1mF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEY6B1mF.png&h=d3f96f96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3d314cda820de63645b14c1de656e536bdd6461","tid":2396313,"uid":245441,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a62f9cd7ef8111bd88f995b6bda24b738b418e74","tid":2396313,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:15:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:16:23.000Z","msg":"本地機組"},{"pid":"2a64a5fef8e2b484dbee98c0ea4a0d7a541fe160","tid":2396313,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:16:42.000Z","msg":"咁貨機計唔計在內？"},{"pid":"3bcb8ca8d666186d155434daf734b7d2108f23b5","tid":2396313,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:17:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e0f6a32a5abaeebf8787b8247e9c61c070ab34","tid":2396313,"uid":389613,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:17:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">不論離開定堅守都係手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span> </span><br />\n<br />\n決意堅守陣地既手足，必須時刻警惕提防，保留有用之軀，日後方能煲底相見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我認為中共已撕破臉皮，唔會再講法理情，只餘硬碰硬一著，而港共武裝與抗爭者實力相距太大，難成氣候，除非把抗爭層面擴大化，將火魔、簡易組裝槍械等等變成家家戶戶都有的必備品，否則難以對抗如同送頭，亦無必要，而且傳播該類資訊卻係十分頭痛既議題，能參與者的數量亦成疑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"> <span class=\"red\">今次 BNO 大量港人走資走人逼中共支爆發難，借東風，引天下圍中，百國聯軍，打柒老共，核平北京，唯一出路！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 離開不是逃避，係主動攬炒救香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>警號已經響起咗！越著時間過去，離開香港將會日漸困難，大時代中不能存有饒幸之心，成日同自己講冇事既、冇事既個d人，就係走唔切，困咗係東德既人。<span class=\"red\">總之任何人，有得即走，特別高風險人士一定要最早走，其他人遲極唔可以遲過外國撤僑，外國第一個國家撤僑你就要跟住飛。外國唔會一次過撤，會比時間同signal香港人走先。</span>切記你係難民唔係移民。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪好好奇美國點解得把口唔出手制裁？我話你知幾時先制裁、有冇可能封關、應唔應該走、幾時要走。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2093986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2093986</a><br />\n<br />\n(分析)仲有幾耐入東突(新疆)模式，見到咩警告要流亡？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1980175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1980175</a><br />\n<br />\n香港簡易流亡手冊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/478029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/478029</a><br />\n<br />\n[借古鑑今] 中國因逃亡潮於 1951 年 2 月 15 日鎖關，香港因 BNO 鎖關的憂慮正響歐美之間蔓延！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2390806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2390806</a>"},{"pid":"44cb35db632de771c5f8dafaa6b58697e6b46eed","tid":2396313,"uid":321913,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:17:31.000Z","msg":"班航空公司仆街喇<br />\n一係停飛<br />\n一係請返D空姐空少"},{"pid":"38bd29ff8800983161070ce70bda7c344852d816","tid":2396313,"uid":36470,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T13:18:17.000Z","msg":"番1日放21 日 要請幾多人 🙊"},{"pid":"80b53f98b